			"value": "<p><em>Armor (Large Shield) - Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p>You gain a +2 bonus to Armor Class against ranged attack rolls while you wield this Shield. This bonus is in addition to the Shield's normal bonus to AC.</p><p><strong>Reaction</strong></p><p><em>Trigger: Whenever an attacker makes a ranged attack roll against a target within 5 feet of you</em></p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>Become the target of the attack instead.</p></li></ul><section id=\"secret-n4z3GTIVyxRRS17N\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Arrow-Catching Shield</strong> effect is provided for optional use and may be toggled active before a ranged attack roll is made against the wearer.</p></section>",
